263
00:17:17,580 --> 00:17:18,580
Aku?

264
00:17:19,580 --> 00:17:21,319
Kamu tidak bisa?

265
00:17:21,420 --> 00:17:22,690
Itu...

266
00:17:23,249 --> 00:17:24,789
Bukan begitu,

267
00:17:25,420 --> 00:17:27,759
