Janji?

280
00:18:17,279 --> 00:18:20,450
Halo? So Hyun, ada kabar penting.

281
00:18:20,450 --> 00:18:22,410
- Kamu sudah tahu soal ini?
- Apa?

282
00:18:23,350 --> 00:18:25,219
Astaga. Baiklah.

283
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:31,319
Ji Yoon, Jung Hyo hamil.

