00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:40,830
Jung Hyo tidak masuk sekolah karena dia hamil.

285
00:18:40,870 --> 00:18:43,229
Teman-teman, Jung Hyo hamil.

286
00:18:43,229 --> 00:18:45,170
