299
00:19:27,709 --> 00:19:30,279
- Benar?
- Ya, Bu.

300
00:19:32,519 --> 00:19:34,049
Sudah selesai.

301
00:19:40,390 --> 00:19:41,759
Sampai jumpa.

302
00:19:46,360 --> 00:19:47,370
"Alamat Bibi Hee Jin"

303
00:19:47,370 --> 00:19:49,370
"20-351, Geolpo-ro, Gimpo-si, Provinsi Gyeonggi"

304
00:20:00,140 --> 00:20:03,279
Perutku sakit, jadi, aku tidak bisa makan.

305
00:20:03,279 --> 00:20:05,150
Kamu membuka restoran sekarang?

306
00:20:05,850 --> 00:20:09,190
- Ya.
- Aku ingin pesan semangkuk bubur.

307
00:20:19,130 --> 00:20:22,930
Selesai sudah penerbangan ini.

308
00:20:23,469 --> 00:20:25,539
Mari kita lihat.

309
00:20:26,299 --> 00:20:28,209
Kamu cemas seharian ini,

310
00:20:28,239 --> 00:20:30,269
