332
00:21:49,190 --> 00:21:52,160
Anda salah kira.

333
00:21:53,219 --> 00:21:55,090
Salah mengira? Apa maksudmu?

334
00:22:05,670 --> 00:22:07,110
Kamu merasa sedih?

335
00:22:09,340 --> 00:22:10,479
Ya.

336
00:22:14,450 --> 00:22:15,950
Ingin aku temani?

337
00:22:18,380 --> 00:22:19,380
Tidak.

338
00:22:19,850 --> 00:22:21,450
Aku akan pergi sendiri saja.

339
00:22:22,749 --> 00:22:24,920
Baik, aku akan menunggumu di sini.

340
00:22:59,690 --> 00:23:01,729
Astaga, bagaimana bisa dia hamil?

341
